item.description:
We discussed moving the date of the meetups to the 4th Thursday of the month.

Thanks to all who brought thier fav photo book! It was fun to see what inspired you.

Also, Please bring any new work you've done over the last few months and share with us. We'd really like to see more photos from you all, so think about making a print or two and bring it along! Or feel free to bring a labtop or web address.

We very much look forward to seeing you and again.
